Signatures: The registration forms must be signed (in some states, online) by one of the organization’s executive officers/directors (e.g. CEO, Chairman, President, Executive Director) and the organization’s chief fiscal officer (i.e. CFO or Treasurer). Please provide the name, title, and e-mail address of the two individuals who will be signing the forms
